<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.6.9">
<l>koṭiya viṉaiyātu milaṉē yeṉṉuṅ koṭiyaviṉai yāvēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ</l>
<l>koṭiyaviṉai ceyvēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ koṭiyaviṉai tīrppēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ</l>
<l>koṭiyā ṉilaṅkaiceṟ ṟēṉē yeṉṉuṅ koṭiyapuḷ ḷuṭaiyava ṉēṟak kolō</l>
<l>koṭiya vulakattīrk kivaiyeṉ collukēṉ koṭiyēṉ koṭiyeṉ makaḷkō laṅkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“I am without any cruel deeds”, she says,</l>
	<l>“and I am the one who is cruel deeds”, she says,</l>
<l>“and I am the one who does cruel deeds”, she says,</l>
  <l>“and I am the one who ends cruel deeds”, she says,</l>
<l>“I have subdued Laṅka with [its] cruel [king]”, she says,</l>
	<l>while the one with the cruel bird settles in [her]?</l>
<l>Why will I say these [words] to you of the cruel world,</l>
	<l>about the beauties of my daughter, the creeper of me who is cruel?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
